# TDD and Traceability

- Treat `@docs/test-plan.md` and `@docs/traceability.md` as the source of truth for tests.
- For any behavior change, start by:
  - locating relevant `FR-*` / `NFR-*` / `INV-*` / `SAFE-*` IDs in `@docs/plan.md`, `@docs/spec.md`, or `@docs/traceability.md`
  - selecting or adding `TC-*` entries in `@docs/test-plan.md`
- Prefer adding or updating tests before implementing code:
  - unit: `TC-U-*`
  - integration: `TC-I-*`
  - contract: `TC-C-*`
  - end-to-end: `TC-E2E-*`
  - security/perf/quality: `TC-S-*`, `TC-P-*`, `TC-Q-*`
- When suggesting changes, mention the exact IDs you are satisfying and where tests should live (file and `TC-*`).
- Do not invent new ID schemes; only extend the existing series.

